AEGON INTERNATIONAL
June 29, 2017
Simona Halep
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT








S. HALEP/T. Pironkova
6-7, 7-6, 7-5
Q. Talk us through the match.
SIMONA HALEP: It was a tough match.  She's just playing really well, but I'm happy that I could finish.  It was important that I could fight till the end and to finish with the victory.
Q. You were rain delayed from yesterday.  How did you manage?
SIMONA HALEP: It's not easy to wait when it's raining, but we are in the same situation so I don't complain and I don't find excuses.
I managed well, because today I could win.  I'm just happy about that.
Q. What will you do to prepare for the next match?
SIMONA HALEP: Just resting.  I will have a stretch, a little bit treatment, and then I will see what I can do in the afternoon.






END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT